sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant EnvoyGW as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant vLLMDecode as vLLM Decode Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLMPrefill as vLLM Prefill Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant ZMQ as vLLM KV-Events<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,vLLMDecode: Flow 1: Standard Inference Request Routing

    Client->>EnvoyGW: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext
    EnvoyGW->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC plaintext
    Note over EPP: Filter pipeline:<br/>by-label, decode-filter
    Note over EPP: Scorer pipeline:<br/>load-aware, prefix-cache,<br/>session-affinity
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool, Pods<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Pod list & status
    EPP-->>EnvoyGW: ProcessingResponse<br/>(selected pod endpoint)
    EnvoyGW->>vLLMDecode: Forward request<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP plaintext

    Note over Client,vLLMPrefill: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (P/D)

    Client->>EnvoyGW: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext
    EnvoyGW->>EPP: ext-proc ProcessingRequest<br/>gRPC plaintext
    Note over EPP: pd-profile-handler selects<br/>decode + prefill pods
    EPP-->>EnvoyGW: ProcessingResponse<br/>+ x-prefiller-host-port header
    EnvoyGW->>vLLMDecode: Forward to decode pod<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP
    vLLMDecode->>vLLMPrefill: Prefill request<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP plaintext
    vLLMPrefill-->>vLLMDecode: Prefill result
    vLLMDecode-->>EnvoyGW: Inference response
    EnvoyGW-->>Client: Response

    Note over EPP,ZMQ: Flow 3: KV-Cache Event Tracking

    ZMQ->>EPP: KV-cache events<br/>ZMQ SUB 5557/TCP plaintext
    Note over EPP: KV-Cache Indexer updates<br/>cache state for prefix-cache-scorer

    Note over EPP,HFHub: Tokenizer Download (startup)

    EPP->>HFHub: Download tokenizer model<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP TLS 1.2+ / HF Token
    HFHub-->>EPP: Tokenizer artifacts
